Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:13.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:19.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:26.76,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:30.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:33.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:02.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:11.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:13.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:15.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:19.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,130.389)}The Monstrous Saigang's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,700.389)}Deadly Auto Race
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How was our time, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking better and better...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But you need a little\Nmore to win it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How much more do we\Nhave to get it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At least two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:02:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's easily won with times\Nlike that in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Mr. Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he's been saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't tell him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,\Nyou need to drive your heart out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so you won't have any\Nregrets, even if you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru is doing\Neverything he can, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's desperate to win and go to\NAmerica, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if he gets to America,\Nhe can fix Tadashi's legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you stand a\Nchance at the win, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, give it a lap, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In preparation for tomorrow's\NAll-Japan Auto Race qualifiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:40.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi and Taki Kazuya are up early\Nto get their last training session in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:45.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, in Shocker's base,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:49.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami,\Nwho had arrived in advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,was awaiting the arrival of the monstrous\NSaigang from Shocker's Africa Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigang hasn't appeared yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Have patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigang will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Gate three here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is a prefectural\Npolice patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:14.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's a motorbike rushing your\Nway at 200 kilometers per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,200 kilometers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.09,Italics,,0,0,0,,Stop it at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... that must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Saigang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you call me to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, who is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isao Katsumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taking part in\Nthe race beside Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigang,\Nyou must bring him here to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The bike's running great, Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You might just win and get\NTadashi to America, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He threw a fit about wanting\Nto come to Izu with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want to restore\Nhis legs to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to run a good\Nrace, even if I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Katsumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Katsumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:04:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Motor Communications.\NCould I have an interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to see Tadashi\Nin the hospital, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi and Tokko\Nbrought this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo says he hopes\Nyou get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's getting interviewed\Nby a newspaper man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Interviewed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But he'll be back\Nsoon, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, lie down and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isao Katsumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You will henceforth\Nbe loyal to Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is your role?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Work with Saigang and destroy\NShocker's enemy, Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, move the plan into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Katsumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished tuning up your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I suddenly wanted\Na race with Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow him a\Nminute, Mr. Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go then, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're raring to go, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Katsumaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My machine's acting up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a Shocker monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Saigang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Saigang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.08,Italics,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:33.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.02,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:39.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.53,Italics,,0,0,0,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,He's going to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to die, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami... why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you finish Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Are you telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He held onto a tree\Ngrowing out of the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such a failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no room for\Nerror when fighting Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You must defeat Hongo\Ntomorrow, even if it kills you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it sting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried for\Na minute there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Some strange gas knocked me\Nout, but I'm better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a fair fight\Ntomorrow, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:47.75,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\3c&HA6BFC2&\c&H000000&}East Japan Road Race Qualifiers\N{\c&H170085&}East Izu One Lap Rally \N{\c&H000000&}Sponsored by J{\c&H170085&}A{\c&H000000&}O\NAdditional Support: {\c&H170085&}Suzuki Automotive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the bike running?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just great.\NLeave the maintenance to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hongo, better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shocker's still after you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they'll probably\Ntry something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a good race.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your places!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get to the pit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru,\Nthat's not the right way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Katsumaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?\NExplain it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.42,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't have any time to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:50.64,Italics,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A formidable foe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, be careful!\NShocker's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- What? \N- They've gotten to Katsumaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Katsumaru?\N Let's just get back\Nto the race for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he off doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.58,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an9}Hongo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Katsumaru!\NKatsumaru's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru,\Nyou're three minutes behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fill me up, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mr. Hongo's gasoline!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A little gasoline won't\Ndecide the victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But he sure is running behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here! It's Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Emi, the gasoline!\N- Hurry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both running behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shocker.\NKatsumaru is working with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- What did you say? \N- Where's Katsumaru, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He came through\Nthirty minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'll get that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, what's happened\Nto the gasoline?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.09,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an9}Hongo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki accidentally put it\Ninto Katsumaru's bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.59,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, it's Katsumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get\Nhim off that bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsumaru! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,His wounds don't seem too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker must have\Nbrainwashed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigang...\NI'll get you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.07,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.60,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:24.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:28.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:31.92,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:35.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:38.23,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:46.16,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:49.56,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:20:00.35,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:04.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:07.61,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:11.14,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:18.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:24.72,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:28.97,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:32.63,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:50.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:54.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:57.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:01.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:04.58,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.63,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:16.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigang, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\Nhis weak point is his horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Drill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, we're just five\Nminutes out of first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We can still win this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see them!\NIt's Mr. Hongo and Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:28.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H000000&\3c&H9DCDBA&}Eto Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:31.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Tadashi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tadashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:45.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9}For Tadashi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:48.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,"Tadashi...\Nthis is a ticket to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:54.04,Italics,,0,0,0,,Go fix your legs,\Nand show everyone how much you can walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.67,0:22:55.91,Italics,,0,0,0,,Promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:57.97,Italics,,0,0,0,,From a friend of\Nyour brother's."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:01.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The deadly race was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:05.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker hadn't given up on\Ntheir plans for world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:07.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Keep fighting, our Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:10.97,Cont,,0,70,150,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:14.40,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:14.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:16.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Semiminga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:21.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Semiminga emits killer sound waves\Nwhich throw the city into chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:23.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and his battle with the Kamen Rider\Ntakes them to the top of Shocker Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:31.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In "The Monstrous Semiminga's\NSong of Slaughter!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:31.20,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)}The Monstrous Semiminga's\NSong of Slaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:41.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:43.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.69,0:23:45.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:51.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:52.95,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.95,0:23:54.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:56.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:04.33,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.33,0:24:07.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:11.47,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.97,0:24:15.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Saigang's\NDeadly Auto Race